extendedInfo.description: Honeycomb PRO released! Supports app2sd, has lots of icons, 10 backgrounds and much more! Search for honeycomb pro go launcher or click the more apps from this developer link.This is the lite version of the honeycomb theme for GO Launcher EX, includes honeycomb icons, dock bar, 5 backgrounds and folder++.1. You must have GO Launcher installed.2. To apply the theme within GO Launcher EX : MENU >preferences >theme preferences3. To change icons: Long press an icon > Replace > Theme's icons > Honeycomb ThemeCheck out our other themes!Keywords : GO Launcher EX theme GO Launcher Dev Team Honeycomb Theme Urtegata

reviews.title: runs smooth, clean design...
reviews.comment: I believe this Go Launcher Theme runs well for a simple Android phone that i have (LG Optimus Net LGL45C). But it is missing the Contacts icon in the task bar. So I had to replace another icon with the Contacts icon. Also doesn\'t allow you to move the app to SD card so there for it takes up some more internal memory of what little I have in this phone that is used up mainly from System apps that can\'t be removed or moved to another source. PLZ add \"Move to SD card\" feature to the app soon.
